	\begin{tabular}{@{}lccc@{}}
		\toprule
		\textbf{Visualization} & \textbf{Clarity (1-5)} & \textbf{Unique Value}           & \textbf{Minima Detection} \\ \midrule
		Bloch Sphere           & 2                      & No parameter optimization shown & No                        \\
		State City             & 3                      & Solution quality visible        & Partial                   \\
		Cost Landscape         & 5                      & Optimization surface visible    & Yes                       \\
		Circuit Diagram        & 5                      & Ansatz structure visible        & No                        \\ \bottomrule
	\end{tabular}
\end{table}

\begin{figure}[h]
	\centering
	完整的QAOA可视化见附录图~\ref{appendix:qaoa}。
\end{figure}

\subsubsection{VQE (Variational Quantum Eigensolver)}

VQE finds ground state energies by minimizing the expectation value $E(\theta) = \langle\psi(\theta)|H|\psi(\theta)\rangle$.

\textbf{Key Findings:}

\begin{itemize}
	\item \textbf{Energy Landscape} shows minimization trajectory toward ground state
	\item State City demonstrates amplitude shift toward ground state basis states
	\item Circuit Diagram reveals hardware-efficient ansatz structure
\end{itemize}

\subsection{Simulation-Based Algorithms}

Simulation-based algorithms emulate quantum system dynamics under Hamiltonians.

\subsubsection{Rabi Oscillation}

Rabi oscillation demonstrates coherent population transfer between quantum states under resonant driving:

\begin{equation}
	|\psi(t)\rangle = \cos(\Omega t)|0\rangle - i\sin(\Omega t)|1\rangle
\end{equation}

\textbf{Key Findings:}

\begin{itemize}
	\item \textbf{Bloch Sphere Trajectory} shows the state vector rotating on the sphere surface
	\item \textbf{Dynamic Flow} reveals time evolution through multiple time points
	\item Z vs Time plot quantifies the oscillation period
\end{itemize}

